### 5. UI — Teacher Dashboard

---

#### [NEW] `src/components/admin/TestManager.tsx`

Replaces the existing `TestManager` (if any). Features:
- **Upload tab**: Two file pickers (`questions.json`, `answers.json`) with live preview of parsed questions count and validation warnings
- **Test list table**: Title, Batch, Subject, Questions count, Attempts, Status
- Clicking a test opens a drawer:
  - View all attempts sorted by score (leaderboard style)
  - "Publish Results" button (for `manual` mode tests)
  - Toggle active/inactive

